#> (Intercept)        -2.0586     4.0386   -0.51                 0.61    
#> flipper_length_mm   0.2151     0.0212   10.13 < 0.0000000000000002 ***
#> speciesChinstrap    8.7801     0.3991   22.00 < 0.0000000000000002 ***
#> speciesGentoo       2.8569     0.6586    4.34             0.000019 ***
